/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無睇F1<br />\n入彎就炒啦"},{"pid":"f7117225efbf4dcb4628f18c8892988c7a0cc13d","tid":205839,"uid":61516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T13:12:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去櫃員機隔離研究下班女人個腦係咪裝屎先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌呢個真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b0ef1e173e57ee2316233a2fe13e0ac13e5d0c6","tid":205839,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T13:17:51.000Z","msg":"Sexist af no la <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34efe0d137d2582a5033c2db44a09205e7269066","tid":205839,"uid":2503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T13:25:16.000Z","msg":"Google, Facebook, Microsoft, Apple, Tesla, Whatsapp, Instagram 全部都係男人創造<br />\n<br />\n此post已完"},{"pid":"c4992dd6f4f43d1570bf3f6049cb5885d8e8cd49","tid":205839,"uid":21629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T13:31:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n掃描結果發現平均而言男性大腦比較大，但是女性的大腦皮質次區域比男性大，這個區域掌管記憶、感官輸入、<span style=\"font-s